# ===========================================================================
# GeoHam-MambaCD v3-fix: Spatial SSM + Cross-Attention + ChangeAggregator
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CHANGES FROM v3 (which regressed to 0.8362):
#       Row-wise SSM scan → back to spatial mean (correct for 16×16)
#       TemporalCrossAttention (fixed pre-norm, clean residuals)
#       ChangeAggregator (SE-style per-scale gating on skips)
#       Energy conservation: temporal variance across steps (not .var())
#       CrossAttn: norm4 removed, pre-norm pattern applied consistently
#       ChangeAggregator: scale_attn input was malformed in suggestion
#       GroupNorm groups: safe for all EfficientNet-B2 channel counts
#       AMP: compatible with both old and new PyTorch
#       TOPO_WEIGHT: per-dataset dict, wired into loss + training loop
#       FOCAL_ALPHA: per-dataset dict, wired into loss + training loop
#       Threshold grid extended to [0.30 ... 0.80]
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

